name: TaskStatus
description:

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.attempt_dispatch_count
params.description: Output only. The number of attempts dispatched. This count includes attempts which have been dispatched but haven't received a response.

params.name: data.attempt_response_count
params.description: Output only. The number of attempts which have received a response. This field is not calculated for [pull tasks][google.cloud.tasks.v2beta2.PullMessage].

params.name: data.first_attempt_status
params.description: Output only. The status of the task's first attempt. Only [dispatch_time][google.cloud.tasks.v2beta2.AttemptStatus.dispatch_time] will be set. The other [AttemptStatus][google.cloud.tasks.v2beta2.AttemptStatus] information is not retained by Cloud Tasks. This field is not calculated for [pull tasks][google.cloud.tasks.v2beta2.PullMessage].

params.name: data.last_attempt_status
params.description: Output only. The status of the task's last attempt. This field is not calculated for [pull tasks][google.cloud.tasks.v2beta2.PullMessage].
